imdb.plot outline: Tells the story of 6 men from different social background that work at a cargo company and they are dismissed unjustly due to a restructuring of the company. This is why they decide to join forces and get even with their former employer. They decide to heist a truck and steal the merchandise so they can sell it and split the profits. When they start to like this new adventure, they make the horrible mistake of getting the attention of a dangerous mob boss known as "The Chilean" who has been a victim of the pushovers. However, the worst is yet to come because of whom they are really petrified are of their wives and girlfriends who have no idea on what their sweeties are involved in. These 6 men may be top dogs in the street but when they get home, they become tame little puppies.
imdb.title: Peleles
plot: When a group of men are fired from their jobs, are tempted to steal trucks to get money.::Anonymous
